Package eu.profinit.manta.connector.erstudio.model

Interface LogicalDataModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataModel, Layered, eu.profinit.manta.dataflow.generator.modeling.common.nodes.NodeMetadata
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LogicalDataModelImpl
    public interface LogicalDataModel
extends DataModel
    Interface providing access to a database model created with higher level of abstraction of its objects. Its underlying objects that are of type CompositeDataObject represent logical Entities.
